message.entry: Index ports should be of data type int8, int16, int32, uint8, uint16 or uint32.
Fraction ports should be of data type double or single.
All index ports should have the same data type.
All fractions ports should have the same data type.
The data types of 'Table data' and inputs to fraction ports don't match. Both can be either single or double.
Nearest or Flat interpolation method only supports clip extrapolation method.
Dimension of 'Table data' can not be smaller than interpolate dimension.
Each breakpoint should have at least two values.
Table data cannot be complex value.
Input signals cannot be complex value.
Input values to index ports cannot exceed the maximum index of the breakpoints.
Input values to index ports cannot be less than 0.
Input values to fraction ports can be greater than or equal to 1 only when index is maximum.
Input values to fraction ports can be negative only when index is zero.
